      "content": "\"Look upon them, these scattered tribes, and see not men, but rather untamed beasts inhabiting a patch of earth! Their customs are mere instincts, a chaotic sprawl devoid of true reason or governance. They require firm stewardship, a guiding hand strong enough to drag them from this primal mire into the light of proper society. We are not merely visitors; we are the necessary architects of their ascent, the shepherds of these wild souls.\"",
      "source": "target",
